like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲物價冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地香港人去到變富豪<br />\n鬼佬去到個個變誠哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想買層樓去當酒店 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d33cd9eee0df1dfba3cf7a1a61ac8003e9c0259","tid":382232,"uid":5892,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊去8日 $4000夠唔夠 唔計機票同住 <br />\n學生窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n機票酒店選擇飛唔靚時間酒店住啲3星酒店<br />\n預要2000蚊 另外2000蚊洗費唔買野 <br />\n只係食 坐車 玩<br />\n咁就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地話唔計機票同住宿<br />\n<br />\n4000蚊喺泰國可以洗到好豪"},{"pid":"579314e9dee27d509b6eca547504677e94b787c7","tid":382232,"uid":5892,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:10:02.000Z","msg":"泰國呢個地方真係一去愛上<br />\n好想好似胡慧沖咁搬過去生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531e1d01b83ae39d7432c1f7eeeae07f0f8afe95","tid":382232,"uid":94182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:23:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>黎緊去8日 $4000夠唔夠 唔計機票同住 <br />\n學生窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n機票酒店選擇飛唔靚時間酒店住啲3星酒店<br />\n預要2000蚊 另外2000蚊洗費唔買野 <br />\n只係食 坐車 玩<br />\n咁就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地話唔計機票同住宿<br />\n<br />\n4000蚊喺泰國可以洗到好豪</blockquote><br />\nSorry 眼殘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁4000一定夠啦 豪洗都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我今次去玩五日 洗費4000<br />\n 剩係打靶場都食咗我1000hkd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e5b6837fbbeabbc56f6d44e1c08db53f6aa15c4","tid":382232,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:26:31.000Z","msg":"天氣又好過濕鳩香港"},{"pid":"e810b1ee826d6cbb0de55ddec84373076bb182d2","tid":382232,"uid":94182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>泰國呢個地方真係一去愛上<br />\n好想好似胡慧沖咁搬過去生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去住就唔同講法<br />\n如果要我長住同生活<br />\n我一定會接受到 玩就冇問題<br />\n日日對住啲神廟鬼怪<br />\n同埋始終覺得東南亞文化唔係咁接受到"},{"pid":"604091b620e2d6535d52270dede44be4b844bcd7","tid":382232,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:27:17.000Z","msg":"叫雞又平"},{"pid":"58b17dbb261b65aa5a6c9e9d1d293c79ee328b94","tid":382232,"uid":11418,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:29:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊去8日 $4000夠唔夠 唔計機票同住 <br />\n學生窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你要睇下機票啦<br />\n8日⋯⋯⋯4000蚊仲要未包機票酒店<br />\n個人認為有d危⋯咩都扣曬你得番小小錢旁身<br />\n到時有咩事你咩都無架啦"},{"pid":"de6eb56b8fb4f955ec922f194e1666cf371b762c","tid":382232,"uid":11418,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T03:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊去8日 $4000夠唔夠 唔計機票同住 <br />\n學生窮遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你要睇下機票啦<br />\n8日⋯⋯⋯4000蚊仲要未包機票酒店<br />\n個人認為有d危⋯咩都扣曬你得番小小錢旁身<br />\n到時有咩事你咩都無架啦</blockquote><br />\n自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇錯野⋯原來係「唔計機票酒店」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n8日4000夠架啦<br />\n<br />\n唔好晚晚落蛇美就得架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00