g":"泰國人服務業好有禮貌"},{"pid":"e1b681f6d3f496ff8b5760fc75e337458c7cb849","tid":382232,"uid":53139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:55:10.000Z","msg":"有冇達人可以簡單評論下泰國熱門個幾個城市有咩特色？<br />\n未去過泰國。黎緊下次想去。但又心思思唔知去邊個城市好"},{"pid":"3bc94d5b5a7a111e642b5fcb319422a2c9983b61","tid":382232,"uid":141041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:56:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3ca87393b608fbf2de43271408ce0b0481e69a22","tid":382232,"uid":141041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T04:56:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebd17ececfdec005c6d3acaac94e599851d63a9c","tid":382232,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T05:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861bc9751b9d26bec924786d11e8430272033f9e","tid":382232,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正到痴線 清邁啲野平到癲<br />\n係衰在交通無咁方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n清萊清邁係咪要自駕/包車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a2a64903d58389c4bc3e9fbd46fa67bf0345c0","tid":382232,"uid":40725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T10:45:11.000Z","msg":"曼谷就不了，無下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n清邁好好多，hea得快樂，啲嘢又平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82620a9be028c51c7193d2498f59cd538b24c854","tid":382232,"uid":109629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T12:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>9月第一次去清邁一星期休息下，<br />\n巴打有無咩景點活動好介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我今年一月頭都去左清邁 有幾樣野個人覺得幾好玩幾特別係到推介下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 大笨象體驗營</strong><br />\n活動內容主要係餵大笨象食野，幫佢沖涼，影下相咁<br />\n可以零距離接觸大笨象係幾難忘既體驗<br />\n<br />\n係到要特別提提大家千其唔好join果啲有<span style=\"color: red;\">騎大笨象</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">睇大笨象畫畫</span>環節既tour，呢類活動業者背後會用好殘酷既手法黎train大笨象畫畫，同埋大笨象成日比人騎會騎到佢d骨畸形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以記得要搵標榜不騎大象／大笨象保護園背景既活動業者黎join<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">參考資訊：<br />\n價錢：我係kkday到買約HKD500一個人包接送，午餐，飲用水<br />\n活動業者名稱：Elephant Jungle Sanctuary<br />\n利申：非打手，建議大家自己搵多幾間格價</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 泰菜烹飪班</strong><br />\n去得泰國應該都會鐘意食泰菜啦<br />\n呢類烹飪班會有人教你煮泰菜 活動完結仲送本當日煮過既菜式食譜比你<br />\n雖然我玩完之後返香港都冇自己煮過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">參考資訊：<br />\n價錢：唔記得<br />\n活動業者名稱：Mama Noi 唔知乜廚藝學校，d老師都幾nice同搞笑 成個教煮野食過程係好順暢，冇冷場／odd位 臨尾仲食到勁飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n照舊利申：非打手<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. Zip line</strong><br />\n係個森林入面玩飛天鋼索，d樹好撚高成6／7層樓咁高，好撚刺激好正<br />\n有人會concern東南亞玩呢啲活動會唔會有風險<br />\n我玩果間d平台同鋼索睇落好新淨企落好穩，d教練都好著重安全<br />\n有兩個安全扣，教練幫你換安全扣上鋼索飛出街之前都會好小心咁check<br />\n總之玩完個feel係唔錯事後大tip特tip左個教練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">參考資訊：<br />\n價錢：HKD300－400左右<br />\n活動業者名稱: Flying Squirrel 咁上下唔係好記得<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 景點類<br />\n清萊果邊既白廟黑廟都ok，d建築係幾靚<br />\n清邁市區都冇乜特別景點，係去下夜市食下野買下零食手信咁（好撚平）<br />\n所以唔join tour出去玩下係會幾悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢啲大路景點詳情自己search，唔多講<br />\n講住咁多先，如果有巴打想知多啲／睇下相先再覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後，join local tour如果有得揀prefer語言：中文／英文 <br />\n記得揀英文，我諗你都唔想同成班蝗一齊玩成日掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"3466fe0c38fbb92cbf0e1b181659cfb8addd55fc","tid":382232,"uid":109629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T12:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次去7日痾撚左6日 on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我果次去瘋狂鳩食路邊野食足一星期都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a267f69f506610ecf5e4053628ef66484be3fb81","tid":382232,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:14:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=56&amp;v=j-_UY4NM1j4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D56%26v%3Dj-_UY4NM1j4&d=v%2BAlg%2BW9BTXNfQ5RjVNRLTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=301e3b70\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=56&amp;v=j-_UY4NM1j4</a><br />\n<br />\n貼下泰文歌先  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3282725cac039cc3e32bf330f3814607336a08c","tid":382232,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T14:17:18.000Z","msg":"鬼妹唱泰國傳統歌<br />\n<br />\nChristy Gibson 泰國好紅，識講流利泰文架 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gi73zLYVPhM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGi73zLYVPhM&d=v%2BAlg%2BW9BTXNfQ5RjVNRLTOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=8c00b85f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gi73zLYVPhM</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d199825d3835055acb1e6a5bbb310f563644306b","tid":382